  # Get Submission by ID

  Returns a single submission record.

  ## Path Parameters

  | Param | Description |
  |-------|-------------|
  | id | Submission identifier (e.g., `sub-001`, `sub-002`, `sub-003`) |

  ## Response Shape

  ```json
  {
    "id": "sub-001",
    "systemId": "system1",
    "modelId": "deepseek-r1",
    "submissionDate": "2026-01-15T10:30:00Z",
    "publishDate": "2026-03-16T00:00:00Z",
    "resultValid": true
  }
  ```
